msgstr "交换机与管理"

msgid "Not attached to a bridge"
msgstr "未加入网桥"

msgid "Persistent port assignment"
msgstr "持久化端口分配"

msgid "Allow PXE clients to access the upstream network"
msgstr "允许 PXE 客户端访问上游网络"

msgid "Disabled by default. When enabled, only PXE-to-management forwarding and NAT are added."
msgstr "默认关闭。启用后仅添加从 PXE 到管理网络的转发与 NAT。"

msgid "Select a PXE dedicated port before enabling upstream access."
msgstr "请先选择 PXE 专用端口，再启用上游访问。"

msgid "Apply port assignment"
msgstr "应用端口分配"

msgid "The selected PXE port is already active."
msgstr "当前已经使用所选的 PXE 端口。"

msgid "Restore all ports to switch mode"
msgstr "恢复全部网口为交换机模式"

msgid "Confirm PXE port change"
msgstr "确认切换 PXE 端口"

msgid "PXE services will stop and all four physical ports will join the management switch."
msgstr "PXE 服务将停止，四个物理网口都会加入管理交换机。"

msgid "The selected port will immediately leave the management switch and become the dedicated PXE port. LuCI, SSH and mDNS will no longer be reachable through that port."
msgstr "所选网口会立即离开管理交换机并成为 PXE 专用端口，之后无法再通过该网口访问 LuCI、SSH 或 mDNS。"

msgid "If this management session uses the selected port, the page will disconnect. Move the management cable to another port. This setting has no automatic rollback."
msgstr "如果当前管理连接正在使用所选网口，页面会断开。请把管理网线移到其他网口。此配置不会自动回退。"

msgid "Restore switch mode"
msgstr "恢复交换机模式"

msgid "Apply PXE port"
msgstr "应用 PXE 端口"

msgid "Failed to save the PXE port configuration."
msgstr "保存 PXE 端口配置失败。"

msgid "Applying network configuration"
msgstr "正在应用网络配置"

msgid "The configuration was saved and the network is restarting. Reconnect through any remaining switch port if this page becomes unavailable."
msgstr "配置已保存，网络正在重启。如果页面无法访问，请通过其余交换机网口重新连接。"

msgid "Failed to update PXE upstream access."
msgstr "更新 PXE 上游访问失败。"

msgid "PXE upstream access enabled."
msgstr "已启用 PXE 上游访问。"

msgid "PXE upstream access disabled."
msgstr "已关闭 PXE 上游访问。"

msgid "Enable PXE upstream access"
msgstr "启用 PXE 上游访问"

msgid "PXE clients will be routed through NAT to the management network. They will still be blocked from device management services."
msgstr "PXE 客户端将通过 NAT 访问管理网络，但仍无法访问设备管理服务。"

msgid "Serve boot files directly from any rclone remote over a read-only HTTP data plane. The selected PXE port remains isolated and no USB disk is required."
msgstr "通过只读 HTTP 数据面直接提供任意 rclone 远程存储中的启动文件；所选 PXE 端口保持隔离，且无需 USB 硬盘。"

msgid "Cloud PXE is configured but will not start until a PXE dedicated port is selected in PXE Settings."
msgstr "云端 PXE 配置会被保留，但只有在“PXE 设置”中选择专用端口后才会启动。"
